        public int length1

      • redundancy

        public boolean redundancy
        Sets the reader to read the barcode twice before accepting data. 

         Example Usage:

      • verifyCheckDigit

        public ScannerConfig.VerifyCheckDigit verifyCheckDigit
        Check the integrity of all Code 11 symbols to verify that the data complies with the specified check digit algorithm. This selects the check digit mechanism for the decoded Code 11 bar code. Use enum ScannerConfig.VerifyCheckDigit. 

         Example Usage:
 	code11.verifyCheckDigit = VerifyCheckDigit.NO;

      • reportCheckDigit

        public boolean reportCheckDigit
        Transmit Code 11 data with or without the check digit. 

         Example Usage:
 	code11.reportCheckDigit = false;
